# Build-context exclusions for the brew-v6 spike image. Mirrors
# docker/sandbox/.dockerignore — the current Dockerfile uses only
# `COPY --from=` (no copy from the build context), so this file is
# forward-looking: any future Dockerfile change that introduces
# `COPY <ctx> ...` benefits from these exclusions.

# Standard housekeeping.
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
.vscode/
.idea/
